author: @sonalisamal2009
text:
Their outfit and style is so good here. They look absolutely breathtaking in this attire. The last part where I think it's The8 and Mingyu dancing as a duo/couple was really neat and beautiful. This MV looks like some responsible rich men have gathered together on this yacht, to celebrate one of their friends getting married, or it's like a group reunion between school/college friends. The location is so beautiful as well. I love everything about this MV. I really appreciate the investment, hardwork that goes into making such beautiful content. So proud of Seventeen and the team. 

P.S: Jeonghan, you just take my breath away. Joshua, so pretty ❤

author: @sonalisamal2009
text: Seventeen really is the best. I love many artists and appreciate their talent, but no other artiste has made me so happy, like Seventeen has. I feel a deep connection with their music on a personal level, and generally relate with them on a soul level. Seventeen really is the artist that feels like home to me, a refuge I can keep coming back to, or more clearly a home that I would hardly leave behind. I'm blessed that I came across Seventeen and I'll always be grateful. I'll always love and support these 13 beautiful men. Once a Carat, always a Carat. ❤
